The Indebted are the main workforce on the 400 moons. Some of them take up arms, either to rebel against their Void Baron overlords, or in their service.

Designed for 6mm/8mm gaming in mind. Compatible with games such as Adeptus Titanicus or Battletech.

You'll save 40% when buying these as a bundle rather than separately.

This package contains the four existing kits:
1) [Armed Indebted (rifles)](https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/game/smallscale-rifle-armed-worker-gang)
2) [Armed Indebted (close combat)](https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/game/smallscale-close-combat-brutes)
3) [Armed Indebted (pistols)](https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/game/smallscale-gunslingers)
4) [Armed Indebted (flamethrowers)](https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/game/smallscale-flame-troopers)
5) [25mm round bases](https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/game/25mm-round-bases-for-6mm-8mm-miniatures-tech-shanty-texture) (extra inserted bits not included)

All armed gangers are either on 5.8mm round inserts or without such inserts. Note that the 25mm bases are just the bases, not the insert detail bits from the separate kit.

Please do not share or sell these files (including prints and remixes) without my written permission.

The Empire of Sentient Man has the diverse army taking part in permament war against the foul traitors and treacherous aliens. Mostly, the army is represented by ill-equipped militia in various ballistic armour (including coats), wielding only laser rifles. Red Militia has such a tragic fate. While being the defenders of their land, they have to reach the planets too far beyond comprehension, test the mud with their boots and treads and hope for weapons to beat unfamiliar threats.

The Red Militia models, with faces diminished and bases added, are shared for free with the permission of NotANiceGuy (https://cults3d.com/en/users/NotANiceGuy/3d-models).

The pack contains:
- command squad including lieutenant, communication officer, standard bearer and sergeant;
- line infantry in 8 different poses;
- heavy weapons teams with heavy machine gun, automatic gun, laser cannon, missile launcher;
- random loaders and mortar crew;
- plus non-Red Militia 3 commissars and 2 psykers.

UPDATE 2023.08.15:

- Master of Discipline model added;
- All the Red Militia are downscaled to fit 8mm scale;
- All the weapons on carriages are downscaled;
- New Missile Launcher team for nostalgic feels.
